      </div>

    </div>
    <div class="grid__item">


      <div class="how-it-works__text-description">

        <h3>HOW IT WORKS</h3>

        <ul>


          <li>
            <span class="circle">
1
          </span>
          
          <span>FILL OUT 2-MINUTE STYLE QUIZ
            AND SHARE YOUR LOGOS</li>

          <li><span class="circle">
2
          </span>

          <span>
            APPROVE FREE CUSTOM DESIGNS
